{"tid":1984562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"忌：鬧黃絲食 m 記貪方便；宜：鬧藍屍食 m 記崇洋","createTime":"2020-04-22T13:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T17:55:47.000Z","uid":147226,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec1c7e933ca5de676763ade8b4ec298e67a1984d","tid":1984562,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"黃絲食唔食 m 記我完全無興趣知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍屍食 m 記，就係崇洋，向美式國物脆低，唔愛中國。正宗藍屍日日去美心酒樓食一盅兩件，做唔到就唔該唔好話自己愛國愛港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你曾經用過幾分鐘時間去討論黃絲應唔應該食 m 記，麻煩你用返兩倍時間去批鬥藍屍食 m 記崇洋，唔理你挑藍屍親戚機又好，用扮藍屍嘅 account 入 save hk 講又好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，你嘅時間更應該係用响 twitter 戰線，支持蘋果日報等等"},{"pid":"69699bea2bb39a762dd16e63e90294e25ebcbd08","tid":1984562,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"如果你曾經用過幾分鐘時間去討論黃絲應唔應該食 m 記，麻煩你用返兩倍時間去批鬥藍屍食 m 記崇洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9212a7bb2ca152e17a14f9670cddfcc42455800c","tid":1984562,"uid":259988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"用Iphone崇洋<br />\n唔用簡體字係港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550c4cde7ca42be05057b7b7a894234034651358","tid":1984562,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659a9512693c78161203bbdffe19097ddc1666f9","tid":1984562,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"都得"},{"pid":"0f85b9ed17af020bbbed573b08df2e011fb8187f","tid":1984562,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"9fb880ffec38d57c0fbf8b2f9bb6c33eb2f253c6","tid":198456